These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, billiard, scrabble, mah-jongg
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, grey, fuchsia, aquamarine
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, siglo, dunhill, game
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, thriller, scientific
1. the person who likes grey is the person playing chess##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
6. the cain-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
7. the person who likes grey is the person watching comedy movies##1
8. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game         | chess  | mah-jongg  | billiard | scrabble |
| Color           | grey | light-blue | aquamarine  | fuchsia  |
| Cigar   | game       | dunhill      | cain | siglo      |
| Movie-Genre           | comedy          | martial-arts     | thriller    | scientific     |

