.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, boat, train, trike
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, chinese, russian, canadian
City: miami, london, new-york, san-francisco
4 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, guinea-pig, snake
1. the spanish is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the russian is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
6. the person driving the train is the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person driving the van##1
9. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Transport      | train     | van       | boat | trike        |
| Nationality          | canadian     | chinese       | russian   | spanish   |
| City   | new-york      | london       | san-francisco     | miami    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | snake | lizard | frog |

