.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, january, december
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, oliveros, blend, ritmeester
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, lily, poppy, balloon-flower
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, emerald, purple, brown
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who likes brown##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
 3. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 7. the person who growslily is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Birthday      | february | august       | december        | january        |
| Cigar           | oliveros   | blend | montecristo   | ritmeester |
| Flower   | iris     | lily    | balloon-flower | poppy        |
| Color           | purple         | apricot  | brown       | emerald         |

