4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, bongani, davidoff, bluemaster
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, rock-climbing, puzzles, chess
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the palace house##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Birthday           | august   | june  | february | march |
| House   | tower | gothic-revival       | palace       | ranch-style     |
| Cigar   | davidoff       | bluemaster    | bongani     | baccarat  |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing     | puzzles | chess     | photography         |

