.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, ship, tram
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, hot-chocolate, lemonade
4 different games are played: poker, snooker, monopoly, billiard
City: boston, london, hamburg, liverpool
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person playing poker is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
9. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Transport           | boat  | ship    | snowmobile | tram |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | sprite    | mirinda         | lemonade    |
| Game   | snooker   | poker     | monopoly          | billiard      |
| City         | london | boston | liverpool      | hamburg      |

