The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, baseball, soccer, golf
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, cooking, video-games, chess
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, dahlia, iris, aconite
 1. the polish is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 2. the nigerian is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 4. the person who growsiris is the nigerian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's sport is golf##1
 6. the polish is on the left of the russian##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Nationality          | nigerian  | malaysian | polish     | russian |
| Sport           | soccer  | golf      | cycling | baseball    |
| Hobby   | cooking | video-games  | dancing    | chess  |
| Flower           | iris   | aconite       | bellflower       | dahlia      |

