5. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
8. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
9. the person traveling to paris is the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
